data.description: Stunning contemporary home on over a private acre lot, boasting 3 bedrooms, 3.5 baths and captivating winter views of the Cumberland Plateau through expansive walls of windows.  Enjoy privacy and the beauty of nature from the full length deck accessed from the formal dining area and the primary bedroom.  Home features include cathedral ceilings and french doors, double oven in gourmet kitchen.  The main level hosts a wood-burning fireplace, while the primary bedroom offers a luxurious bathroom with a huge soaking tub.,  Stay comfortable with the recently installed HVAC system , approx 5 year old roof and benefit from extra storage in the large walkout basement.  Dont miss the convenience of deck access from the primary bedroom and the modern design throughout this exceptional property.
